@startuml Login & Session â€” User Level
title Login & Session Management

actor "User" as user
participant "Login Page" as login
participant "Dashboard" as dash
participant "Any Protected Page" as page

== Successful Login ==

user -> login : Navigates to /login
user -> login : Enters email and password
user -> login : Clicks "Sign In"
login -> dash : Redirects to /dashboard
user -> dash : Sees personalised dashboard\nwith org stats and nav sidebar

== Session Persistence ==

user -> page : Navigates to any page\n(e.g. /products)
page -> page : Page loads normally\n(session still valid)

== Session Expiry ==

user -> page : Returns after inactivity
page -> login : Automatically redirected\nto /login
note right of login : Session expired.\nUser must log in again.

== Invalid Credentials ==

user -> login : Enters wrong password
login -> login : Shows "Invalid credentials" error
user -> login : Can retry

@enduml
